title: DUPLEX FOR RENT
map_address: 5149 ROCKY HILL DR near GARNER RD
posting_body: Here is your rare opportunity to rent a multi-family brick duplex property in a safe and upscale neighborhood!

Unit A is Vacant and Unit B will be vacant on August 31st, Each unit has 2 bedrooms, 1 baths., living room, dining area, kitchen, washer/dryer hookups, private deck, big driveway for off road parking, front porch overlooking nice  big yard.
Cable and Internet services are available in the area.
Units are currently being updated but are in good condition READY for move in now.
All units are attached to each other and are under one roof.
Rent is priced below market for the area.
